}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "TS-419U II V1.1", "FKN-20006-A011920YS-RS" and "QV08" are silkscreened on the board.
===Hardware specification=== *CPU: [[Marvell]] 88F6282 @2GHz (''Kirkwood'' ARM V5) *Memory: 512MB (SDRAM) DDR3 *Storage: 16MB Flash, 4x SATA II, 2x eSATA *Network: 2x Gigabit Ethernet port *USB: 4x USB 2.0 Type A *Power: 120-240V AC via C13
